  "texts": [
    "Our results highlight the relative advantage of Claude2 in neuro-adolescent growth and developmental assessments compared to other LLMs.",
    "This exceptional performance may be attributed to several unique factors of Claude2, such as its extensive parameter set, continuous feedback from a vast user base and collaborating experts informing its training, advanced reasoning and directive tracking abilities, recent training data, and integration of insights from actual applications of these prior models into Claude2's safety research and monitoring systems, all contributing to more accurate responses.",
    "Interestingly, all three LLM chatbots were equally capable in providing comprehensive responses.",
    "The top 10 'Poor' questions illustrate that all three chatbots gave detailed answers to complex questions that challenge human doctors, further demonstrating the capability of LLM-Chatbots to provide relevant and detailed information.In our assessment of 10 prevalent adolescent diseases, all LLM chatbots showcased commendable performance in answering questions about disease progression, particularly excelling in areas of 'Anxiety Disorders' and 'Depression' as detailed in Table 4.",
    "Yet, a signi cant variation in performance was observed in 'Sleep Disorders' and 'Tic Disorders', as indicated in Table 2."
